Nigerian singer, Paul Play Dairo, has shared his opinion on men who are unfaithful in their marriages. Taking to his official Instagram page, Paul Play said men who are ready to cheat on their wives should also accept to be cheated on. He warned men who hide under tradition to cheat to beware of women of today. He wrote: “If you are ready to CHEAT on your wife, be ready for her to CHEAT on you, tradition ko !trabaye ni. “The Bible says love your neighbor as yourself . If you think you can hide under tradition and start behaving anyhow . Today’s woman no send you . You go hear am!” His comment is coming after Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, stirred controversy online after he unveiled his second wife and their son.